    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile, the credibility package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a complete documentation artifact. All 13 credibility factors have been enumerated and their status recorded. Seven factors were formally assessed; six epistemic gaps were identified and documented consistent with MRL 5 requirements. The package satisfies Minimal profile structural requirements. Note: achieved levels fall below required levels for all assessed factors, confirming the original Not Accepted engineering determination; however, the package itself is accepted as a valid credibility evidence submission under the Minimal profile binding rules.",
